I noticed that the Pervasives module does not offer a function
round : float -> int
implementing the useual rule: if the the fractional part is 
greater than or equal to 0.5, round up; otherwise round 
down. Of course it can be implemented easily, but should it 
not simply belong to the Pervasives module?

Alex

